    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>Pressurized jets breathe additional oxygen into the Jetpack flames, brightening and lengthening the exhaust trail.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>高压气体将为喷气背包的尾焰添加额外氧气，使得尾气痕迹更加明亮且持久。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>加壓噴射器吐出額外氧氣到噴射背包火焰中，增亮並延長排氣尾跡。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
